name: Cyber Eltanin
desc: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned (from your hand) by banishing all LIGHT Machine-Type monsters from your side of the field and your Graveyard, and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. This card's ATK and DEF become the number of monsters banished for its Special Summon x 500. When this card is Special Summoned: Send all other face-up monsters on the field to the Graveyard.
